CHANGES
=======

0.10.0
------

* integration test: run manage-projects with debug
* Test manage-projects repos harder
* Handle newer Gerrit ls-groups command syntax
* Handle empty reads as closed connections
* Avoid crash due to POLLIN event check
* Fix package metadata
* Allow custom retries on gerrit connection
* Decouple linters from unit testing
* Add support for TCP keep alive in gerritlib

0.9.0
-----

* Add branches arg to createProject
* Fixed linting issues
* Replace testrepository with stestr
* Enable py36-py38 testing
* Added missing retry\_delay instance variable
* Use ensure-\* roles

0.8.4
-----

* Run gerritlib integration tests with python3
* Return lists from listing functions

0.8.3
-----

* Pass Gerrit not GerritConnection to GerritWatcher
* Add integration testing with jeepyb and gerrit

0.8.2
-----

* Convert gerrit output to utf8 unicode
* Use newer paramiko
* Support querying for single group info
* Reuse same paramiko connection recreating on errors
* OpenDev Migration Patch
* Replace openstack.org git:// URLs with https://

0.8.1
-----

* Close ssh connections when done with them
* Updated list of Python versions in tox

0.8.0
-----

* Add group membership management functions

0.7.0
-----

* Handle different gerrit versions with create-project
* Remove pyflakes environment
* Removed pbr<2.0.0 to resolve depencency conflicts
* Remove deprecated create-project '--name' option
* Allow creating projects with spaces
* Specify testenv command for tox>=2.5

0.6.0
-----

* Cap paramiko<2.0.0
* Stop specifying requirements.txt in tox.ini
* Bump pbr and hacking version

0.5.0
-----

* Update project docs
* Doc generation support
* Workflow documentation is now in infra-manual
* Switched documentation to point to storyboard
* Update listGroups function in gerrit.py
* Python3 support
* Add functionality to Gerritlib to set project descriptions
* Changed home-page used in setup.cfg
* Update pbr version
* Apply cookiecutter defaults

0.4.0
-----

* Add empty-commit flag when creating a project with no commits
* add getVersion and listPlugin commands and update replicate command
* remove extra item from listGroups and listProjects methods
* Quote group names in case of spaces
* Expose the gerrit watcher as a thread with defined transitions
* Allow startWatching to take in watcher connection limits
* Add connection attempt limit

0.3.0
-----

* Add replicate command
* Remove erroneous comment
* Remove use of d2to1
* Allow ctrl-Cing gerritlib programs
* Ignore editor files
* Simplify GerritWatcher creation

0.2.7
-----

* Add method to list Gerrit Groups

0.2.6
-----

* fix param ordering to fix review function
* Add comments option to query
* Add option to query commit messages
* Remove dependency on distribute
* add a bulk\_query method to let us get back more than one item
* Modernize build requirements
* Updated .gitreview location

0.2.5
-----

* Remove dangerous dbQuery method

0.2.4
-----

* Add owner option to createGroup
* Remove sitepackages=true

0.2.3
-----

* Fix gerrit create-project option order

0.2.2
-----

* Ignore versioninfo file
* Add createGroup and require\_change\_id option

0.2.1
-----

* Add create and list projects calls

0.2.0
-----

* Add Gerrit DB query method to gerritlib
* Supply port to GerritWatcher

0.1.0
-----

* Fix description
* Add Apache2 license file to the project
* Add a project wide .gitignore
* Add setup.py to project
* Add gitreview
* Add start actions
* Use paramiko for stream-events
* Remove stray print statements
* Fix logic error in reporting
* Initial commit
